    Simple Flashlight App - Privacy Policy
    Owner: VenomXxX
    Mail: vx65559@gmail.com

    Effective Date: [17.11.2024]

    Thank you for using Simple Flashlight App. Your privacy is important to us. This Privacy Policy explains how we handle your data and permissions. By downloading and using this app, you agree to the terms outlined here. If you do not agree, please do not use the app.

    Data Collection
    - No Personal Data Collection:
      Simple Flashlight App does not collect, store, or share any personal data.

    - Non-Personal Data:
      The app may collect anonymous usage data (e.g., app crash logs) for improving functionality. This data cannot identify you.

    Permissions
    - Camera Access:
      The app requires access to your device's flashlight, which is controlled through the camera hardware. This permission is solely for turning the flashlight on and off.

    - Internet Access:
      No internet access is used or required by the app.

    Data Security
    - Your data is never shared, sold, or used for any purpose outside the intended functionality of the app.

    Third-Party Access
    - The app does not display ads or include links to external websites.

    Disclaimer
    The app is provided "as is." While we strive to ensure its functionality, we do not guarantee uninterrupted or error-free operation. VenomXxX is not liable for any issues or damages resulting from its use.

    Changes to This Policy
    We may update this Privacy Policy as necessary. Any changes will be reflected with a new "Effective Date."

